headline: McKesson (MCK): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: McKesson currently trades at $660.88 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 402% since March 2020, more than tripling the S&P 500’s 118% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 38%.
